-------------------------**************************------------------------
				WIFI RC_CAR
-------------------------**************************------------------------
				DESCRIPTION

--> Controller(left,right,forward,backward) RC Car With Mobile App
--> Stream Camera

-------------------------**************************------------------------
				API KEY

--> WiFi Server http://192.168.4.1/?MakerCar=
API : Speed=100,Buzzer=1,Servo=1,Controller=1,LedCam=1,
--> Keyword 
	+ Speed : from 0 to 100 (%) normal speed*2.53
	+ Buzzer: sw(bz) : 0 -> OFF , 1 -> ON
	+ Servo : from 40 to 110 (left -> right) // Maybe use
	+ Controller : from 0 to 9
	+ LedCam : sw(lc) : 0 -> OFF , 1 -> ON

-------------------------**************************------------------------
				CONTROLLER INFO
--> Servo <--- 
	+ 55 	--> Forward Left & Backward Left
	+ 30	--> Left
	+ 110 	--> Right
	+ 95	--> Forawrd Right & Backward Right
	+ 80 	--> Forward & BacWard

--> Controller <--
	+ 1	Forward 
	+ 2	Backward
	+ 3	Right
	+ 4	Left
	+ 5	Forward Left
	+ 6 	Forward Right
	+ 7 	Backward Left
	+ 8	Backward Right
	+ 9	Stop

